\033[1m\033[32mLIST\033[0m - List all scripts in a mango repository

\033[1mUSAGE:\033[0m
    mango @list [repo_path]

\033[1mDESCRIPTION:\033[0m
    Lists all scripts and their bound commands in a mango repository.
    If no path is provided, searches from the current directory upward for the closest repo.
    Displays the script name and associated commands in a formatted table.

\033[1mARGUMENTS:\033[0m
    repo_path    Path to the mango repository to list (default: current directory)

\033[1mEXAMPLES:\033[0m
    mango @list
    mango @list ~/my-project